Privacy Policy
Introduction

This Privacy Policy will explain how we collect, use, disclose and protect your information upon using
our mobile application.

Information We Collect and Use
We may require you to provide us certain personal information, including but not limited to user's name, contact number,
address, sexual identity, and pictures. The information that you will provide will be kept by us and will be used on the following purposes.

We will use the information in the following purposes, including:
    To provide and process transactions
    To personalise and manage your account
    To provide updates and status of transaction
    To verify and prevent fradaulent transactions

We also want to inform that users will also have an access to these personal information with other, specifically laundry shop owners to verify the person who will make the transactions. However, they are obligated to use and share
these information on any other purposes.


Privacy Policy Changes
We may update our policy from time to time. Any changes on the privacy policy will be published on this page.
Therefore, we suggest you to review our privacy policy periodically for any changes.

